title: Super Spendthrift
summary: Super Spendthrift Raw What would you do if you become rich overnight? This might be a daydream that everybody has thought of. But for our FL, his dream came true. He woke up and become the son of the Duke Li in Ming Dynasty. This young master is a well-known spendthrift and has indulged himself in numerous beauties. Do you think our FL will live in this lifetyle? Wrong! With knowledge in the future, he is ambitious to make some contributions and engrave his name in the Chinese history!
